Table.Command: SELECT (SELECT TOP 1 "MainCurncy" FROM OADM) AS "LocalCurrency", T3."Currency" AS "BpCurrency", T0."CreateDate", T1."DunAddr", T2."CardCode", T2."DocNum", T2."DueDate", T2."DocType", T2."LetterLvl", T2."OpenCurr", T2."OpenSum", T2."TotalFee", T2."FeeCurr", T3."CardName", T3."LangCode", T4."U_NAME" AS "User", T4."PortNum" AS "UserPhone", T4."E_Mail" AS "UserMail", T5."Name" AS "UserBranch", T6."Name" AS "UserDepartment", T2."IntrstAmnt" AS "IntrstAmntLc", CASE WHEN T3."Currency" = T2."IntrstCurr" THEN T2."IntrstAmnt" ELSE CASE WHEN (SELECT TOP 1 "DirectRate" FROM OADM) = 'Y' THEN T2."IntrstAmnt" / (SELECT TS0."Rate" FROM ORTT TS0 WHERE TS0."Currency" = T3."Currency" AND TS0."RateDate" = T0."CreateDate") ELSE T2."IntrstAmnt" * (SELECT TS0."Rate" FROM ORTT TS0 WHERE TS0."Currency" = T3."Currency" AND TS0."RateDate" = T0."CreateDate") END END AS "IntrstAmntFc", CASE WHEN (SELECT TOP 1 "MainCurncy" FROM OADM) = T2."FeeCurr" THEN T2."TotalFee" ELSE CASE WHEN (SELECT TOP 1 "DirectRate" FROM OADM) = 'Y' THEN T2."TotalFee" / (SELECT TS0."Rate" FROM ORTT TS0 WHERE TS0."Currency" = T2."FeeCurr" AND TS0."RateDate" = T0."CreateDate") ELSE T2."TotalFee" * (SELECT TS0."Rate" FROM ORTT TS0 WHERE TS0."Currency" = T2."FeeCurr" AND TS0."RateDate" = T0."CreateDate") END END AS "TotalFeeLc", CASE WHEN T3."Currency" = T2."FeeCurr" THEN T2."TotalFee" ELSE CASE WHEN (SELECT TOP 1 "DirectRate" FROM OADM) = 'Y' THEN T2."TotalFee" / (SELECT TS0."Rate" FROM ORTT TS0 WHERE TS0."Currency" = T3."Currency" AND TS0."RateDate" = T0."CreateDate") ELSE T2."TotalFee" * (SELECT TS0."Rate" FROM ORTT TS0 WHERE TS0."Currency" = T3."Currency" AND TS0."RateDate" = T0."CreateDate") END END AS "TotalFeeFc", CASE T2."DocType" WHEN 13 THEN (SELECT TS0."DocDate" FROM OINV TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") WHEN 14 THEN (SELECT TS0."DocDate" FROM ORIN TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") WHEN 30 THEN (SELECT TS0."RefDate" FROM OJDT TS0 WHERE TS0."TransId" = T2."DocAbs") WHEN 24 THEN (SELECT TS0."DocDate" FROM ORCT TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") WHEN -2 THEN (SELECT TS0."RefDate" FROM OJDT TS0 WHERE TS0."TransId" = T2."DocAbs") WHEN 203 THEN (SELECT TS0."DocDate" FROM ODPI TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") ELSE '19700101' END AS "DocDate", CASE T2."DocType" WHEN 13 THEN (SELECT IFNULL(TS0."DocTotal", 0) FROM OINV TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") WHEN 14 THEN (SELECT IFNULL(TS0."DocTotal", 0) * -1 FROM ORIN TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") WHEN 30 THEN (SELECT SUM(IFNULL(TS0."Debit", 0) - IFNULL(TS0."Credit", 0)) FROM JDT1 TS0 WHERE TS0."TransId" = T2."DocAbs" AND TS0."ShortName" = t2."CardCode") WHEN -2 THEN (SELECT SUM(IFNULL(TS0."Debit", 0) - IFNULL(TS0."Credit", 0)) FROM JDT1 TS0 WHERE TS0."TransId" = T2."DocAbs" AND TS0."ShortName" = t2."CardCode") WHEN 24 THEN (SELECT IFNULL(TS0."DocTotal", 0) * -1 FROM ORCT TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") WHEN 203 THEN (SELECT IFNULL(TS0."DocTotal", 0) FROM ODPI TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") ELSE 0 END AS "DocTotal", CASE T2."DocType" WHEN 13 THEN (SELECT IFNULL(TS0."DocTotalFC", 0) FROM OINV TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") WHEN 14 THEN (SELECT IFNULL(TS0."DocTotalFC", 0) * -1 FROM ORIN TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") WHEN 30 THEN (SELECT SUM(IFNULL(TS0."FCDebit", 0) - IFNULL(TS0."FCCredit", 0)) FROM JDT1 TS0 WHERE TS0."TransId" = T2."DocAbs" AND TS0."ShortName" = T2."CardCode") WHEN -2 THEN (SELECT SUM(IFNULL(TS0."FCDebit", 0) - IFNULL(TS0."FCCredit", 0)) FROM JDT1 TS0 WHERE TS0."TransId" = T2."DocAbs" AND TS0."ShortName" = T2."CardCode") WHEN 24 THEN (SELECT IFNULL(TS0."DocTotalFC", 0) * -1 FROM ORCT TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") WHEN 203 THEN (SELECT IFNULL(TS0."DocTotalFC", 0) FROM ODPI TS0 WHERE TS0."DocEntry" = T2."DocAbs") ELSE 0 END AS "DocTotalFC" FROM ODWZ T0 INNER JOIN DWZ1 T1 ON T0."WizardId" = T1."WizardId" INNER JOIN DWZ2 T2 ON T0."WizardId" = T2."WizardId" AND T1."CardCode" = T2."CardCode" INNER JOIN OCRD T3 ON T2."CardCode" = T3."CardCode" INNER JOIN OUSR T4 ON T0."UserSign" = T4.INTERNAL_K LEFT OUTER JOIN OUBR T5 ON T4."Branch" = T5."Code" LEFT OUTER JOIN OUDP T6 ON T4."Department" = T6."Code" WHERE T0."WizardId" = {?$[BOY_DUNNING_WIZARDID]} AND T2."CardCode" = N'{?$[BOY_DUNNING_CARDCODE]}' AND T2."LetterNum" = {?$[BOY_DUNNING_LETTERNUM]} AND T2."ChckLine" = 'N' ORDER BY T2."DocNum" DESC
